data.description: Discover the epitome of comfort and space in this inviting single-story home nestled within the vibrant community of City Heights, San Diego.  No HOA!  This charming 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence offers an expansive lot, perfect for those who appreciate outdoor living and gardening.  As you step inside, you'll be greeted by an open and well-lit living space with ample room for relaxation and entertainment. The kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances and ample cabinet space, making it a delight for any culinary enthusiast.  The two spacious bedrooms offer tranquility and comfort, and the two well-appointed bathrooms provide convenience for residents and guests alike.  There is a basement as well for your creative ideas.  The real gem of this property is the generous lot that surrounds the home, providing endless possibilities for outdoor enjoyment. Whether you dream of creating a lush garden, a play area, or even an outdoor oasis, this blank canvas awaits your personal touch.  Conveniently located in the heart of City Heights, you'll have easy access to shopping, dining, and local amenities, all while enjoying the peace and privacy that this generous lot provides.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this delightful single-story property your own and experience the best of City Heights living!
